	<p>
	<tag/Paste/
	Paste the contents of the clipboard as a new image (if the clipboard contains a valid icon).
	<p>
	<tag/Clear/
	Clear the grid and fill it with transparent color.
	<p>
	<tag/Select all/
	Marks the entire icon as selected.
</descrip>

